# Forms (v2) Module Guide

- Base path: `/forms/v2/tenant/{tenant}`.
- Modules:
  - `forms_get_forms`: mirrors Form_GetForms; supports filters `hasConditionalLogic`, `hasTriggers`, `name`, `status`, `ids`, `active`, date filters, pagination, and `sort`.
  - `forms_get_form_submissions`: mirrors FormSubmission_GetFormSubmissions; supports `formIds`, `active`, `createdById`, `status`, `submittedOnOrAfter`, `submittedBefore`, `ownerType`, `owners[]`, and pagination.
  - Jobs attachments helpers: `forms_get_job_attachment`, `forms_create_job_attachment`, `forms_get_job_attachments`.

- Enum handling:
  - `status` (forms): `Any|Published|Unpublished`.
  - `status` (submissions): `Started|Completed|Any`.
  - `ownerType`: `Job|Call|Customer|Location|Equipment|Technician|JobAppointment|Membership|Truck|Project|ServiceAgreement|InvoiceItem`.
  - `active`: `True|Any|False` tri-state.

- Owners param: Expand each owner as indexed pairs `owners[i].type` and `owners[i].id`.

- Responses: pretty-print JSON; concise error string on failure.

